text: Kay A. Orr (born January 2, 1939) was an American politician. She was born in Burlington, Iowa. Orr was the 36th Governor of Nebraska from 1987 to 1991. She is a member of the Republican Party. ==References== ==Other websites== *Governor Orr's papers at the Nebraska State Historical Society *National Governors Association * Category:1939 births Category:Politicians from Iowa Category:Governors of Nebraska Category:Living people Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians
